  📝 HOW TO GET NVIDIA API KEYS:
     1. Go to https://build.nvidia.com/
     2. Sign in with your Nvidia account (you have access)
     3. Navigate to API Keys or Settings
     4. Generate new API keys (can create multiple)
     5. Copy the key and paste into .env
     6. You can have different keys per model if desired

  💡 TIP: You mentioned Nvidia gave you access to many API keys
     └─ You can use the same key for both models
     └─ OR use different keys for rate limit isolation (recommended for scale)


